==制作==
最初11集和12集并未计划在一起播出，但是受到[[颶風桑迪|颶風桑迪]]导致的停播后决定一起播出。Carter Bays说“我们想让第12集作为圣诞节特别集，但是第11集合第12集感觉像是一个故事的两部分，所以让圣诞节特别集延长成一个小时。”<ref>{{cite web |last=Porter |first=Rick |url=http://blog.zap2it.com/frominsidethebox/2012/12/how-i-met-your-mother-ep-carter-bays-teases-the-final-page-and-talks-final-season-plans.html |title='How I Met Your Mother': EP Carter Bays teases 'The Final Page' and talks final-season plans |publisher=Zap2it.com |date=December 17, 2012 |accessdate=December 18, 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121221114715/http://blog.zap2it.com/frominsidethebox/2012/12/how-i-met-your-mother-ep-carter-bays-teases-the-final-page-and-talks-final-season-plans.html |archivedate=2012年12月21日 }}</ref>，在计划合并播出前第11集的标题是“The Silence of the Jinx”而第12集的标题是“The Robin”<ref>{{cite web |last=Fitzpatrick |first=Kevin |url=http://screencrush.com/how-i-met-your-mother-hour-long-holiday-episode/ |title='How I Met Your Mother' Goes Hour-Long for Holiday Episode |publisher=Screen Crush |accessdate=December 18, 2012 |archive-date=2013-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130421083459/http://screencrush.com/how-i-met-your-mother-hour-long-holiday-episode/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

